               (g/expt q/I q/I)
               (g/expt q/J q/J)
               (g/expt q/K q/K))
            "i^i matches quaternion implementation for each of the components.")

        (is (ish? q/K (g/expt q/I q/J)))
        (is (ish? q/I (g/expt q/J q/K)))
        (is (ish? q/J (g/expt q/K q/I))))))

